<h1>UX Research Portfolio</h1>
<p>Biography: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/paulmay/" class="fancy">Paul May</a> is a UX researcher and design strategist who specialises in healthcare applications and medical device design projects. He is currently working with London-based design agency Monokoto.</p>
<p>I'm proud to present a selection of relevant work for your consideration, and would be happy to expand upon this work at any point in the future.</p>
<div id="fyeo">This portfolio has been prepared for Google Health. Please do not distribute this work outside your team without prior permission. Many thanks.</div>
